v 0.1.9
d wttreport: Batch Welch independent-samples t-test reporting pipeline
d
d wttreport runs the complete Welch independent-samples t-test reporting workflow.
d It can process one or more two-category grouping variables and create
d complete per-group reports or component table, figure, summary, results, and mapping outputs.
